@startuml use-case-guest
left to right direction
skinparam usecase {
  BackgroundColor #F7FBF6
}

actor Guest as "Guest (Unauthenticated)"

usecase "Browse Homepage" as UC01
usecase "View Product List" as UC02
usecase "Search Products" as UC03
usecase "View Product Details" as UC04
usecase "Chat with AI" as UC05
usecase "Register" as UC06
usecase "Login" as UC07
usecase "View Categories" as UC08
usecase "Open Login Modal on Add to Cart" as UC09

Guest --> UC01
Guest --> UC02
Guest --> UC03
Guest --> UC04
Guest --> UC05
Guest --> UC06
Guest --> UC07
Guest --> UC08

' Alternate flows notes
note right of UC09
Guest can attempt "Add to Cart";
client should redirect to `/login` or open auth modal.
After successful login, pending action may be replayed.
end note

' Include relations
UC04 .> UC09 : include
UC02 .> UC03 : include

@enduml